                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-620" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM STEPTO</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 111.) The prisoner and the plane were delivered to me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Were the other two boys taken? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I went and found them, and they were taken before Magistrate and discharged—this boy gave the description of them—the prisoner said he was along with them, and that one of them stole it and gave it him to carry.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
